## .NET build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/[Ll]og/
**/[Ll]ogs/

## Node modules (they'll be restored inside the container)
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log*

## React output (will be built inside container)
src/Web/ClientApp/build/

## Visual Studio files
**/.vs/
**/*.user
**/*.suo

## Git
.git/
.gitignore

## Sensitive / environment files — never in Docker context
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

## Test projects (not needed at runtime)
tests/

## Documentation
docs/
README*.md
DOCKER.md
*.md

## CI/CD files
.github/

## Other
artifacts/
diff src/
http src/
